1. How do you agree or consent to this Privacy Policy?
By visiting any of the PNP Sites, using any of the PNP Services, downloading, installing, using or purchasing any Content or PNP Mobile Apps or purchasing any PNP Products, you accept and agree to this Privacy Policy.
In addition, acceptance of this Privacy Policy could be evidenced by a mandatory checkbox process when finalizing the purchase, download, installation or use of PNP Content or Mobile Application or when purchasing PNP Products.
If you do not want to accept and agree, you must leave the PNP Site, refrain from using it and any PNP Services, and refrain from purchasing, downloading, installing, or using any Content or PNP Mobile Apps or purchasing any PNP Products.
We will only use your Personal Information when the law allows us to. If we require your consent, we will request it formally, in adherence to applicable privacy laws.
As noted in this Privacy Policy, we reserve the right to update or alter this Privacy Policy at any time in the future. You should review this Privacy Policy regularly to ensure that you are aware of any changes.
We will take appropriate technical and organisational measures against unauthorised or unlawful processing of your Personal Information and against accidental loss or destruction of, or damage to, your Personal Information.
