Terms of Use
of the applicable third party processor.
•
Your information from affiliates, business partners and other third parties
such as social media third party login (Facebook, Google and AppleConnect, among others) and other third party marketing database partners. We also may periodically obtain both Personal Information (such as contact information) and non-Personal Information (such as demographic information) about you from affiliated entities, business partners and other independent third-party sources and add it to other information that we have collected about you.
•
Your information automatically collected by us when you visit PNP Sites or use PNP Services
. In order to help us understand your interests and customize your user experience, we automatically collect some information about your computer when you visit the PNP Sites, use the PNP Services, or purchase, install or use the Content or the PNP Mobile Apps. For example, we will collect session data, including your IP address, web browser software, and referring website. We also may collect information about your online activities, such as content viewed and pages visited. See also below the discussion of cookies and web beacons.
•
Your information you provide to PNP from Facebook, Google, Apple and other Social Networking Sites
. You may create your PNP account by using a social network site, such as Facebook Connect, Google Connect or Apple Connect, which will allow you to automatically share with us certain Personal Information from your social network account to set up your PNP account. For example, we may obtain the following information from Facebook Connect, Google Connect or Apple Connect: your first name, last name and email address. If you choose to do so, we will store data from your social network account on our PNP servers so that we can use updated data from your social network account. Please refer to the privacy settings of your social network account to determine how you may adjust your permissions and manage the interactivity between the PNP Services and your social network account or mobile device. As noted in the
Terms of Use
, social network sites are third party sites subject to their own privacy policies and
Terms of Use
. Your Submissions of photos, videos and other materials from your social media accounts to your PNP account through the PNP Submissions process, once received by PNP, will be governed by PNP Privacy Policy,
Terms of Use
, and
Terms of Sale
as applicable.
•
Your payment information
. We use third parties, such as PayPal, Stripe, Google Play, Apple Store and Amazon, to process payments, including any credits, rebates, discounts or promotions. Your payment data is sent directly to these third parties and is subject to the privacy policies and
Terms of Use
of the processing third party.
You can choose not to provide us with information, such as to not register or provide us with information for the videos or phone calls or not accept certain cookies as provided for below; however, if you do so, you may not be able to access PNP Site, PNP Mobile Apps or PNP Services or take advantage of certain features of the PNP Sites, PNP Mobile Apps or PNP Services.
